                            <comment id="248951" author="adilger" created="Tue, 11 Jun 2019 05:35:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I suspect the last issue was fixed with &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12248&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_418: df and lfs df inodes output mismatch&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12248&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12248&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="248781" author="gerrit" created="Sat, 8 Jun 2019 02:32:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (green@whamcloud.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/34453/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/34453/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
